PR #2362: [Win32] Lazy load Cursor handles
Changed files (2): bundles/org.eclipse.swt/Eclipse SWT/win32/org/eclipse/swt/graphics/Cursor.java, tests/org.eclipse.swt.tests/JUnit Tests/org/eclipse/swt/tests/junit/Test_org_eclipse_swt_graphics_Cursor.java
